"Low volumes of the economy are the result of several events, including the cold, one of the main effects was a slow economy that doesn't become fast enough to create economic dynamics that allows to have an acceptable level of processes, goods and services and, therefore, at the end of the year we close it below our expectations," he said.
Review of direction
